description: Best Value in Southie! Not To Be Missed! 2 beds, 2 baths, 2 private patios, central AC, and deeded parking all for $719,000?! Stop paying rent and build your own nest egg. This home offers a flexible floor plan all on 1 level! Ideal for roommates. 3rd bedroom is currently used as a dining room, but could easily be converted back. Living room has slider that opens to a private patio -- great for grilling and chilling outside! The main bedroom has double closets, an en-suite bathroom, and a slider that opens to a 2nd private patio. 2nd bedroom is large, with a full bathroom off the hall. The kitchen features Frigidaire stainless steel appliances, gas cooking, subway tile backsplash, and quartz counters. 1 deeded parking space, central AC, deeded storage, a bike room, and common laundry complete the package. Originally built in 2,000 and renovated since, this well-maintained home is freshly painted and move-in ready!
